            <thetext>On the Samsung Galaxy S4 Android Version 4.4, the border-radius is not displayed at all.

I found a description of this bug here:

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/17186158/galaxy-s4-stock-browser-css3-border-radius-support/17695006#17695006

The bug only occurs if the border-radius CSS property are grouped like this:

border-radius: 4px

As this is only a device specific bug, and the Android Update to Version 4.3 will be released soon, we will not apply the bugfix.

But we have to check if this bug still occurs on Android 4.3 before the next release of qx.Mobile.</thetext>
